NSSI Thoughts

Antecedent Model

dat.nssi.thoughts<-data[which(data$Study=="Bresin et al. 2013"|data$Study=="Kuehn et al., In Prep"|data$Study=="Selby and Joiner, 2018"|data$Study=="Kiekens et al"), ]

m.nssi.thoughts.a <- metagen(NSSI.thoughts_A,
                  SP_NSSI.thoughts_A,
                  data = dat.nssi.thoughts,
                  studlab = paste(Study),
                  comb.fixed = FALSE,
                  comb.random = TRUE,
                  method.tau = "ML",
                  hakn = TRUE,
                  prediction = TRUE,
                  sm = "MD")

NSSI Behaviors

Antecedent Model

dat.nssi.behavior<-data[which(data$Study=="Bresin et al. 2013"|data$Study=="Vansteelandt et al. 2012"|data$Study=="Houben et al 2017"|data$Study=="Muehlenkamp et al., 2009"|data$Study=="Kuehn et al., In Prep"|data$Study=="Selby et al., 2013"|data$Study=="Selby and Joiner, 2018"|data$Study=="Czyz et al. 2017"|data$Study=="Kiekens et al"|data$Study=="Santangelo et al., 2017"), ]

m.nssi.behavior.a <- metagen(NSSI.behaviors_A,
                  SP_NSSI.behaviors_A,
                  data = dat.nssi.behavior,
                  studlab = paste(Study),
                  comb.fixed = FALSE,
                  comb.random = TRUE,
                  method.tau = "ML",
                  hakn = TRUE,
                  prediction = TRUE,
                  sm = "MD")
